D) To Show the Data in Descending Order Use below Query 

select id, enrollment_date, selected_course, fname, years_of_exp, student_company, batch_date, source_of_joining, location from students ORDER BY fname desc;


+----+---------------------+-----------------+---------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+-----------+
