|  1 | 2024-07-21 12:01:42 |               2 | rohit   |            5 | walmart         | 05-02-2021 | linkedin          | mumbai    |
|  4 | 2024-07-21 12:07:17 |               4 | rahul   |            8 | amazon          | 05-02-2021 | quora             | delhi     |
|  5 | 2024-07-21 12:13:20 |               4 | kapil   |           15 | microsoft       | 5-02-2021  | friend            | pune      |
