[Data is showing in Descending order on the basis of "fname"]  [Hum aise hi dusre Columns ka name de k kr skte h like years_of_exp]





E) Double Level Sorting 1st on the basis of years_of_exp & 2nd on the basis of fname [virat & shikhar dono ko 3 yrs ka exp h but "S" comes 1st toh shikhar ka name phla aya]

 select fname, years_of_exp from students order by years_of_exp,fname;

+---------+--------------+
| fname   | years_of_exp |
